            <h3>How to Place an International Order</h3>

            <p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Select your desired items (items eligible for international orders listed on our online store).</p>

            <p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Message us on our Facebook Page: <a href="" style="color: #50222b">CD Station</a>.</p>

            <p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Provide your information:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Full Name</li>
                <li>Detailed Address</li>
                <li>Phone Number</li>
                <li>Email Address</li>
            </ul>

            <p><strong>Step 4:</strong> CD Station will create an order for you.</p>

            <p><strong>Step 5:</strong> Payment via PayPal.</p>

            <p><strong>Step 6:</strong> CD Station will process the shipping.</p>

            <p><strong>Step 7:</strong> CD Station will provide you with the receipt of your items from Vietnam Post and refund the shipping fee (if any).</p>
            <hr>
            <h3>Important Notes</h3>

            <p><strong>1. Payments:</strong> PayPal. Listing prices do not include VAT & PayPal Fee (10%).</p>

            <p><strong>2. When will my order ship?</strong> International orders will be shipped on the 5th and 20th of every month.</p>

            <p><strong>3. Delivery service:</strong> CD Station offers worldwide shipping via Vietnam Post.</p>

            <p><strong>4. Delivery time:</strong> Delivery estimates:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Asia Pacific: 1-2 weeks</li>
                <li>Europe: 3-4 weeks</li>
                <li>North America: 3-4 weeks</li>
                <li>South America: 4-5 weeks</li>
                <li>Africa: 5-6 weeks</li>
            </ul>

            <p><strong>5. Shipping fee:</strong> Vietnam Post rates vary based on size, weight, and destination. For more details, contact us via <a href="" style="color: #50222b">CDStation@gmail.com</a> or Facebook Messenger at <a href="" style="color: #50222b">CD Station</a>.</p>

            <p><strong>6. Customs:</strong> Customs fees, tariffs, or duties are not included in pricing. Orders may be subject to customs fees upon arrival.</p>

            <p><strong>7. What if I receive a damaged item?</strong> Contact us immediately at <a href="" style="color: #50222b">CDStation@gmail.com</a> for assistance.</p>

            <p><strong>8. What if my package is lost?</strong> If your package is lost in transit, email us at <a href="" style="color: #50222b">CDStation@gmail.com</a>. We will file a claim and assist promptly.</p>

            <p><strong>9. Returns & Exchanges:</strong> Items are not eligible for return or exchange after 7 calendar days from receipt. For issues, contact <a href="" style="color: #50222b">CDStation@gmail.com</a>.</p>

            <p><strong>10. Delivery notes:</strong> Ensure correct delivery address and availability to receive the parcel to prevent delivery issues.</p>
